    "Moore made a second trip to Europe to focus on French architecture.": [],
    "Along the way, Moore clearly read the work of <a href=\"/violletleduce\">Eug\u00e8ne Viollet-le-Duc</a>.": [],
    "The book resulting from this trip, published in 1890, was <em>The Development and Character of Gothic Architecture</em>.": [],
    "It made his reputation as an architectural historian and teacher.": [],
    "Moore received honorary memberships in the American Institute of Architects and the Royal Institute of British Architects.": [],
